high_descs: Go in front of the toilet
Pick up the soap bar on the flusher
Turn around, go forward, turn right and go to the sink
Put the soap bar into the sink, open the water, wait, close the water and pick up the soap bar
Turn around and go to the dresser, turn right
Put the soap bar on the dresser
anns.task_desc: Wash a soap bar and put it on the dresser

high_descs: Look down and back at the top of the toilet.
Pick up the soap from the top of the toilet.
Turn around, head across the room and turn right.
Rinse the soap in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn left and then turn right at the cabinet beside the sink.
Put the soap on top of the cabinet in front of the tube.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed bar of soap on the cabinet.

high_descs: Move forward to stand in front of the toilet.
Pick the soap up from the back of the toilet.
Turn around and then go to the right to stand on the left side of the sink.
Put the soap in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the soap back up.
Turn around and face the white cabinet with the blue trash can to the left.
Put the soap down on the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put soap on top of a cabinet.
